{"type": "article", "id": 22891, "title": "维密将在上海开第一家直营店，以及，Rihanna新鞋今天开售 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-02-26T09:59:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3531, "name": "维多利亚的秘密"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 10258, "name": "Estée Lauder"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 24017, "name": "Robert Pattinson"}, {"id": 1466, "name": "Hermès"}, {"id": 3132, "name": "Emilio Pucci"}, {"id": 3078, "name": "Max Mara"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 2944, "name": "伦敦时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 125, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120837wIYLnGm0WxHrEFUT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b>维多利亚的秘密将在上海开出第一家直营店 | </b>这是维密在美国、加拿大和英国之后在第四个国家开设直营店，\r\n\r\n此前中国的维密店铺均由马来西亚的 Valiram Group 代理，所以我们只能在中国买到维秘的香水、配饰、美容护理产品及副线 Pink 的底裤。之前我们已经报道过，店铺地址位于上海淮海中路上的力宝广场，原店铺地址为 LV，LV 将在后天撤店，维密开店日期暂未定。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b>Burberry 宣布合并男女装大秀 | </b>创意总监 Christopher Bailey 表示将把一年四场大秀（2 月、9 月的女装系列和 1 月、6 月的男装系列）合并成两场大秀。<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/17153.html\">去年我们已经有报道过</a>，品牌将旗下 Brit、London 和 Prorsum 三个系列合并成一个 Burberry 一个品牌。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/christopher-peterson-exit-ralph-lauren-corp-10369617/\">Ralph Lauren 全球品牌总裁辞职</a> | </b>Christopher Peterson 将在今年 5 月 31 日正式离开。昨天，品牌表示 Peterson 将与 CEO Stefan Larsson 完成职责交接。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/gap-sales-weak-eps-meets-expectations-10369360/\">Gap 利润下降 33%</a> | </b>截至 1 月 30 日的第四季度，净利润下降 33% 至 2.14 亿美元，随后股价下跌 3.3%，收盘于 26.70 美元。这一整年的公司盈利下降了 27% 至 9.2 亿美元。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/02/estee-lauder-by-kilian\">Estée Lauder 并购了一个新的奢侈品牌香水品牌</a> | </b>化妆品巨头雅诗兰黛（Estée Lauder）最近收购了一个香水品牌 Frédéric Malle ，是一个九年历史的高端香水品牌，规模不大但从巴黎到莫斯科、多哈的买手店都有售。既有 475 美元 1.7 盎司的\"Pearl Oud\" 香，也有售价 4000 美金 22盎司的\"Prelude to Love, invitation\" 。而创始人 Kilian Hennessy 是LVMH 旗下名酒轩尼诗家族的后代。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/leather-goods/prada-see-now-buy-now-bags-10367958/\">Prada 推出两款“即看即买”手袋</a> |</b> 走秀过后就能在门店中买到，但仅限于伦敦、巴黎、米兰和纽约的指定门店。这两款手袋分别为 the Pionnière 和 the Cahier bags。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031208173z6kwb0MO5cHKRWs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120817cVbr6A3RWpZUEGNF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b><br></b></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>这里有一些伦敦时装周上值得一看的秀场图：</p>\n<p class=\"\">Prada<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120818eXMYcvbWQr6KzEmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Moschino<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120818Av9Ya8IMmUisQKeh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Emilio Pucci<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120820Hz6WGISUicYxZ7ef.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Max Mara<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120821qNfBX3GoHmeVOLAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Fendi<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120822wgAqvi2yIOYbrLJC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.79166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Robert Pattinson 是 Dior Homme 2016 秋冬系列的新面孔。这是品牌第一次在时装广告中使用好莱坞明星，但其实前者从 2012 年以来一直都是品牌香水的代言人。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120823QpwAh2lBdrSGg1xj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120823EimJ3ZM2gkxdyjVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">爱马仕 2016 春夏广告释出，由日籍摄影师 Yoshihiko Ueda 掌镜，广告的拍摄地位澳大利亚科修斯科山国家公园，主题为“Hermès by nature”。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120824x4DQ5ItPsM7fjEcd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120824QINzdMLaRKYshoUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120825ZQhXglFzKIr8VWfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120825nBzSoLgvkaMTNDws.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120826QFoVDJ3znUmwuBtv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34494774\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120826vqf6unUAJbmLZ2w7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34687954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Moschino 推出香烟为主题的胶囊系列，包括一个逼真香烟盒的手机套。这个系列在后天就能于 Moschino.com 上买到。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120826K1YCm7Q8FpOSv3Tt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031208270U5fP4WXyVuO7kCs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120827EkO0qXK6YCeMroGw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120828c5CbQ2TkpgG8lEmv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120829idzTuwJXZKxFV2m4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120829bh78gsn41mcBFqRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312083001WwmxhKavXcjflG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120830Sq0FMZG9PrWldfOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120831G3BtvNTQWOXSkjic.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Raf Simons 与 adidas Originals 又有联名，还是以侧边 R 字为标志，只是变成了清新的苹果绿。售价 455 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120831BitFTqlQ64W38xjN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120831yDOglF5IVk1xU0Cz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Rihanna 的注册商标 Fenty 推出新鞋，这是Rihanna 首款原创鞋款，今天开始发售，可以在\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://rise45.com/collections/new-arrival\">Rise</a> 和 <a href=\"http://us.puma.com/en_US/fenty-trainer-coming-soon?affID=21181&amp;mktID=AFF:21181:PepperJam:2-222496:USA\">Puma</a> 上买到（戳链接）。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120832BJRzWdntg8fLK3UA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120833zn04vKsLcMkXrT1H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120834egafSpnK5MTvdtyZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120834CqAL4j1yuphSQZ3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">又来推荐背包啦，这是来自旧金山的皮件品牌 <a href=\"http://www.octovo.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Octovo</a>，面料选自高级防水材质，肩带部分则采用意大利皮革，内部拥有软垫设计，空间大小足够放入15 吋电脑，折叠设计能根据携带物品的多寡做释放。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120835gBQYEAbIu8JXiVKp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120835B3kuJVzoRFndgO96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120835oCjW1zZQALYcdMwa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120836NfMsdwVIOZhFcn1T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120836vFVsEpuDdyY5RrWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>\n\n"}